whereas.text:
Whereas the USS Lawrence and the USS Niagara, 2 flagships
			 of the fleet of Commodore Perry, were returned to Presque Isle Bay, off the
			 coast of the City of Erie, after completion of their service;

Whereas the City of Erie is home to the USS Niagara, which
			 continues to sail in memory of the heroism of the United States forces in the
			 Battle of Lake Erie;
